Consider a Spring Boot application, 'ABC', that returns the response in various formats. As a developer, you need to develop a code that returns the XML response format of the business requirement 'XYZ'.

Which of the following code snippets will return the response in XML format?

"private static void getResponseAsXML() { HttpHeaders headers = new HttpHeaders(); headers.setAccept(returnType(new MediaType[] { MediaType.APPLICATION_XML })); //Implementation goes here } } }"
"private static void getResponseAsXML() { HttpHeaders headers = new HttpHeaders(); headers.setReturnType((new MediaType[] { MediaType.APPLICATION_XML })); //Implementation goes here } } }"
"private static void getResponseAsXML() { HttpHeaders headers = new HttpHeaders(); headers.setAccept(returnType( MediaType.APPLICATION_XML )); //Implementation goes here } } }"
"private static void getResponseAsXML() { HttpHeaders headers = new HttpHeaders(); headers.setValue(returnType(new MediaType[] { MediaType.APPLICATION_XML })); //Implementation goes here } } }"
